snippet.title: Best of FARM ANIMAL videos - You'll LAUGH FOR SURE!
snippet.description:
Farm animals are so funny, they can make us laugh super hard in no time! This compilation is one of the hardest try not to laugh challenges ever! Just look how all these pigs, goats, horses, chickens,... play, make funny sounds, jump, get stuck,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!

The content in this compilation is licensed and used with authorization of the rights holder. If you have any questions about compilation or clip licensing, please contact us: tigerlicensing@gmail.com

For more funny videos & pictures visit and like our Facebook page:
